A 'broken' parole process: Data shows widened racial bias 
Four years after racial disparities exposed, a state report has yet to be released 
Edward McKinley ,  Amanda Fries 
Nov. 22, 2020 Updated: Nov. 23, 2020 10:44 a.m. 
